<p>I would say that if this is to be your first game, its way, way to complex to finish by yourself <img src="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" />  What you&#8217;ve described is a full time 3 man project for 1 year minimum.</p>
<p>Definitely try to start with something much simpler. As for the language, I would recommend flash with something like flash develop or amethyst, for the reasons I gave in the article.</p>
<p>Hope that helps,</p>
