		<div class="comment-body"><p>Hi there, glad you enjoyed it!</p>
<p>Like I said in the article, the best thing to do is play some old arcade games in mame, get a few ideas and then combine them together into a quick prototype. Aim for a small game &#8211; as small as possible; games are really, really hard to make well, the smaller your goal the better chance you have of completing it!</p>
<p>Cheers, Paul.</p>
